   List of Merlino Keywords                                                     

 G16       : Make G16 Input
 GDV       : Make GDV Input
 CUBIC     : Freq=Cubic(GDV) and Vibr=Gauconv MSR
 NATURAL   : Natural Isotopic Abundance 
 ECKART    : Enforce Eckart Orientation
 IMPDIH    : Use Improper Dihedrals in place of Out-of-plane Bends
 GNIC      : Make Generalized  Natural Internal Coords.
 INVDIST   : Inv.Dist. for Stretching
 SYMMSTR   : Legacy keyword ignored for primitive stretching coordinates
ONEDIH    : 1 Dihedral per Bond (default)
NOONEDIH  : Use all non-ring dihedrals
LOCSVD    : Local SVD GNIC blocks (experimental)
CLEAN     : Clean GNIC values
 LOOSE     : Loose Symmetry for Gaussian
 BDPCS3    : Make BDPCS3 Bond Lengths
 GICSYM    : Symmetrize GIC blocks for downstream modules
 SYCART    : Write symmetrized Cartesian coordinates without changing frame
 SYMMALL   : Symmetrize same-type GNIC blocks (legacy alias)
 FINDFR    : Find Fragments
 JOINFR    : Join Fragments
 HBOND     : Detect H-Bonds as non-covalent targets
 BMAT      : Build B Matrix
 SCAN      : Scan for Soft DOF
 RIGID     : Freeze Hard Modes in Scan
 PCS0      : PCS0 Model (UFF)
 PCS1      : PCS1 Model (HF3C)
 HPCS2     : HPCS2 Model (B3LYP-D4/6-31G*)
 DPCS3     : DPCS3 Model (rev-dsd-PBEP86D4/3F12-)
 OPT       : Geometry  Optimization
 FREQ      : Second Energy Derivatives
 CUBIC     : Third Energy Derivatives
 ANHARM    : Fourth Energy Derivatives (up to ijkk
